1. Ethereum will celebrate its 10th anniversary on July 30, and EF will hold global community events in Shenzhen, Hong Kong and other places;
2. Ethereum spot ETF had a total net inflow of US$602 million yesterday, the second highest in history;
3. The crypto market rose generally, MAG7.ssi rose by more than 6%, and the PayFi sector rose by 17.06%;
4. Backpack has now opened the FTX debt sales channel;
5. The total market value of stablecoins exceeded US$260 billion;
6. Substack completed US$100 million in new financing, with a valuation of US$1.1 billion;
7. A newly created address withdrew 500 BTC from Binance, worth approximately US$59.31 million;
8. Two newly created addresses have accumulated more than 200,000 ETH recently;
9. Hong Kong stocks of stablecoin concept stocks continued to rise strongly for three consecutive days, and OSL Group rose by more than 4%;
10. WLFI increased its holdings 3 hours ago 861 ETH.
